                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/10254" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">FAM-1536</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">341 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">“新华”涅槃，“联”启新程 ——解构新华联“失血-止血-输血-造血”的破产重整之路</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Nirvana of “Macrolink”, New Journey of “Union” —Deconstructing Macrolink&#39;s bankruptcy reorganization path of “bleeding out - stopping bleeding - blood transfusion - blood creation”</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">张敦力，郑丽芳，刘骋宇</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中南财经政法大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">新华联文化旅游发展股份有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">建筑、建材业与房地产业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">财务资产部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">37 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">决策型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">财务困境；破产重整；新华联；文旅地产；2025百优案例</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">financial difficulties、bankruptcy reorganization、Macrolink、cultural tourism real estate</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本案例描述了曾经叱咤文旅地产界的上市公司——新华联，经历“文旅+地产”双轮驱动而快速扩张的高光后，因战略失衡以及行业下行等原因陷入资金链断裂、资不抵债的“失血”困境后启动破产重整。在此困境中，公司通过申请司法预重整、剥离低效资产、实施债务重组实现“止血”；借助资本公积转增股本、引入五家投资人注入资金完成“输血”；通过聚焦核心文旅主业、推进科技赋能、优化成本管控等措施实现“造血”，最终摆脱困境，焕新起航的故事。本案例引导学生探究企业财务困境的深层成因，理解破产重整的前提条件与具体措施，分析重整背景下“资产整合—债务化解—战略转型”的协同作用，探索重整计划顺利进行的原因，深化对市场化法治化重整助力企业重生的认知。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">This case describes the story that Macrolink, a listed company that once dominated the cultural tourism real estate industry, started bankruptcy reorganization after experiencing the rapid expansion of the two-wheel drive of “cultural tourism real estate”, and then fell into the “blood loss” dilemma of broken capital chain and insolvency due to strategic imbalance and industry downturn. In this predicament, the company achieved “hemostasis” by applying for judicial pre-reorganization, divesting inefficient assets, and implementing debt restructuring; With the help of capital reserve to increase share capital, the introduction of five investors to inject funds to complete the “blood transfusion”; By focusing on the core business of cultural tourism, promoting the empowerment of science and technology, optimizing cost control and other measures to achieve “hematopoiesis”, and finally get rid of the predicament and set sail anew. This case guides students to explore the underlying causes of the financial difficulties of enterprises, understand the prerequisites and specific measures of bankruptcy reorganization, analyze the synergy of “asset integration, debt resolution, and strategic transformation” in the context of reorganization, explore the reasons for the smooth progress of reorganization plans, and deepen the understanding of market-oriented and law-based reorganization to help enterprises reborn.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2023</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《财务管理理论与实务》、《并购与重组》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">财务困境理论；不完全契约理论；动态能力理论；利益均衡理论；合作博弈理论</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2025-12</td>
                            </tr>
